# Local Tor client using MixTor as a managed client transport.
#
# Build first:
# cargo build --bins
#
# Then replace the path below if your checkout lives somewhere else.

DataDirectory ./target/local-tor-client-data
SocksPort 127.0.0.1:9050
UseBridges 1
ClientTransportPlugin mixtor exec C:\Users\Thanthal\Documents\Mixtor\target\debug\mixtor-client.exe
Bridge mixtor 127.0.0.1:9001 EF571453EBA73FC10CA3D020817778BF0C6108B3
Log notice stdout
